jspdf 2.5.2
MIT
source: https://unpkg.com/jspdf@2.5.2/dist/jspdf.umd.min.js
file: jspdf.umd.min.js (~360 KB minified, UMD)
choice: UMD bundle — exposes window.jspdf with the jsPDF constructor (window.jspdf.jsPDF). Single-file, no plugins required for the export-pdf workpacket — image embedding (doc.addImage with PNG data URLs) is in the core bundle, no html-to-pdf or autotable plugins needed.
vendored: 2026-04-30 as part of WP-7.4.9c (export-pdf canvas command)

Consumers (present + anticipated):
  server/static/commands/export-pdf.js   — WP-7.4.9c — canvas → PDF export via stage.toDataURL + doc.addImage
  (no other consumers planned at this time)

To refresh:
  curl -sL "https://unpkg.com/jspdf@<new-version>/dist/jspdf.umd.min.js" -o /tmp/jspdf.umd.min.js
  curl -sL "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/parallax/jsPDF/master/LICENSE" -o /tmp/jspdf-license.txt
  cp /tmp/jspdf.umd.min.js  ~/ora/server/static/vendor/jspdf/jspdf.umd.min.js
  cp /tmp/jspdf-license.txt ~/ora/server/static/vendor/jspdf/LICENSE
